quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  6,85,"And Zakariyâ (Zachariya), and Yahya (John) and ‘Îsâ (Jesus) and Iliyâs (Elias), each one of them was of the righteous."
  6,86,"And Ismâ‘îl (Ishmael) and Al-Yasa‘ (Elisha), and Yûnus (Jonah) and Lût (Lot), and each one of them We preferred above the ‘Âlamîn [mankind and jinn (of their times)]."
  6,87,"And also some of their fathers and their progeny and their brethren, We chose them, and We guided them to the Straight Path."